## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

### Three-Tier Architecture

The blog system follows a **three-tier architecture**:

```
┌─────────────────┐
│   Frontend      │  React + React Router
│   (Browser)     │  - Landing.tsx (homepage)
│                 │  - BlogPost.tsx (individual posts)
└────────┬────────┘
         │ HTTPS
         ▼
┌─────────────────┐
│   Server        │  Supabase Edge Function (Hono)
│   (Deno/Hono)   │  - GET /blog-posts
│                 │  - GET /blog-posts/:slug
└────────┬────────┘
         │ Supabase Client
         ▼
┌─────────────────┐
│   Database      │  Supabase Postgres
│   (Postgres)    │  - blog_posts table
└─────────────────┘
```

### Technology Stack

**Frontend:**
- React 18+
- React Router (Data mode)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS v4

**Backend:**
- Deno runtime
- Hono web framework
- Supabase Edge Functions

**Database:**
- Supabase Postgres
- Row Level Security (RLS)

