## 🔌 API Reference

### Base URL
```
https://{projectId}.supabase.co/functions/v1/make-server-38bddc41
```

### Authentication
All endpoints require the public anon key:
```javascript
headers: {
  'Authorization': `Bearer ${publicAnonKey}`
}
```

### Endpoints

#### `GET /blog-posts`
Fetch recent blog posts for homepage display.

**Query Parameters:**
- `limit` (optional) - Number of posts to return (default: 3)

**Request Example:**
```javascript
fetch(`https://${projectId}.supabase.co/functions/v1/make-server-38bddc41/blog-posts?limit=3`, {
  headers: {
    'Authorization': `Bearer ${publicAnonKey}`
  }
})
```

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "posts": [
    {
      "id": "uuid-here",
      "title": "Season 11: Heavenly Forge Support",
      "slug": "season-11-heavenly-forge-support",
      "description": "Full support for Sanctified items and new affixes",
      "tag": "Feature",
      "published_at": "2026-03-05T10:00:00.000Z"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Response (500 Error):**
```json
{
  "error": "Failed to fetch blog posts",
  "details": "error message here"
}
```

---

#### `GET /blog-posts/:slug`
Fetch a single blog post by its slug.

**URL Parameters:**
- `slug` (required) - The post's URL-friendly identifier

**Request Example:**
```javascript
fetch(`https://${projectId}.supabase.co/functions/v1/make-server-38bddc41/blog-posts/season-11-support`, {
  headers: {
    'Authorization': `Bearer ${publicAnonKey}`
  }
})
```

**Response (200 OK):**
```json
{
  "post": {
    "id": "uuid-here",
    "title": "Season 11: Heavenly Forge Support",
    "slug": "season-11-heavenly-forge-support",
    "description": "Full support for Sanctified items and new affixes",
    "content": "<h2>Season 11 is Here!</h2><p>We're excited...</p>",
    "tag": "Feature",
    "published_at": "2026-03-05T10:00:00.000Z",
    "created_at": "2026-03-05T10:00:00.000Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-03-05T10:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

**Response (404 Not Found):**
```json
{
  "error": "Blog post not found",
  "details": "error message here"
}
```

